@node section1 "What is JZ BBS Lister?"

                     @{b}What is JZ BBS Lister?@{ub}

It's really pretty obvious what the door does, it's for Sysops and users to
leave BBS adverts in a list which can be downloaded or displayed by other
users. There is really only 1 other door I know of that does this and thats
the one by Ari Tsironis which I didn't really like. This door is different
in that users get a choice of which sort of compressed list they want, i.e.
LHA, ZIP or LZX or even just a straight text download. Also the screen
which gets displayed can be redesigned by you to fit in with the style of
your BBS!

@{b}Disclaimer@{ub}


